longBusinessSummary: Global Brands Group Holding Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, markets, and sells branded apparel, footwear, fashion accessories, and related lifestyle products for retailers in the Americas, Europe, and Asia. The company offers apparel for kids, men, and women under various licensed and owned brands through department stores, hypermarkets/clubs, off-price retailers, independent chains, specialty retailers, and e-commerce channels. It is also involved in the brand management business, including expertise in expanding its clients' brand assets into new product categories, new geographies and retail, and e-commerce collaborations; and assisting in distribution of licensed products. In addition, the company engages in the research, design, sale, and logistical advice activities; retail sale of cosmetic and toiletry articles in specialized stores, hairdressing, and other beauty treatments; marketing and exploitation of intellectual properties; real estate holding activities; and retailing and wholesaling, import/export, marketing, consultancy, commission agency, and exhibition businesses. Further, it provides media representation, licensing support, management, business process management, payroll, concept development, back office administration, and sourcing services, as well as consultation services for culture communication, investment, enterprise management, and enterprise branding services. Additionally, the company engages in the trading of footwear products; and provision of sourcing services to footwear manufacturers. Global Brands Group Holding Limited was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.
